Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:32.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were merciless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--? M-M-Marriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got guts to marry Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is a giant version of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you make a zombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need to find a zombie in sandals,\NLuffy's giant, and the cook's dogguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our shadows will come back if we\Nthrow salt in their mouths, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly, I'm amazed you\Ndiscovered that weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our info came from that bag of bones,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from how to defeat the zombies\Nto how to rescue you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say, "I got so\Nlonely that I wanted to die"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I would have\Ntaken my own life ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing all of this because\Nyou want to keep a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did you promise your crewmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, we left a member of my\Ncrew behind at a certain location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was unavoidable, yet sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we set sail, we vehemently\Nswore that we would return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then we were annihilated on these seas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,preventing us from keeping our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it has been... fifty years\Nnow since the day we died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years?! Hey, that was ages ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't even born yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:05:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I doubt he's been waiting that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What right do I have to decide\Nwhether or not he's still waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We swore to reunite with my crewmate\Noff some capes. His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt he will forgive us for\Nirresponsibly dying on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a selfish promise
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and died under a distant sky\Nwhere our voices couldn't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry we died" could never cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave our word as men that we would return!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why he's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:06:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Chopper wasn't there for this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Swear to Go See Him!!\NBrook and the Cape of Promise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? How'd you meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin Capes is at the\Nentrance to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A freakishly huge whale was there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I see a mountain up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mountain?! That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a mountain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a black wall!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's a whale!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shall we fight?\N--Idiot! There's no way we can fight that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-But our path is blocked!\NWhat're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...? Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't work! The ship doesn't turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dammit!\N--Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:08:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Did it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... We're screwed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My special seat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here before it's too late!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he not notice the cannon attack\Nbecause his body's too big?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is he just slow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?! Anyway,\Nlet's get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! My ears hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paddle! Just paddle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...! What the hell did\Nyou do to my special seat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:10:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Luffy's silliness,\Nwe got swallowed whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... The whale ate you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was Laboon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. There was an ancient lighthouse\Nkeeper who lived inside the whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flower pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had been treating Laboon from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lighthouse keeper was treating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly he used to be\Nthe medic on a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? But why did he\Nneed treatment? Was he sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was continually bashing his head
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against the Red Line, which is\Nlike a wall dividing our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been waiting fifty years for some\Npirates who promised to come for him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:11:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after they traveled around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But fifty years...? Those pirates sure\Nare making him wait a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! This is the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long he waits,\Nthey won't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's true that fifty years ago\Nthe Grand Line was an uncharted sea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more terrible and chaotic than it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking so hopeless?!\NYou don't know that for sure yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might come back!\NIt's a very touching story!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whale continues to believe in the\Npromise with his friends... Right, pops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But reality is cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed it using reliable information.\NThey ran away... from the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be... Don't tell me...\Nthey left without him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they are alive,\Nthey'll probably never come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seasons. Weather. Current. Wind direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all random. Common sense\Nis useless in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The terror of the Grand Line takes\Nover weak minds in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They abandoned this whale?!\NWhen he's been waiting for fifty years...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that, why haven't you told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That whale can understand\Nwhat people say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did tell him... everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Laboon! They're not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you don't wanna accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you somehow have to accept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's since then that he started\Nhowling at Reverse Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that he started slamming\Nhis body against the Red Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if he's insisting that they'll come back\Nfrom the other side of that wall any time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there's no point in waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He refuses my words because if he accepts them,\Nit means that there is no point in waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:14:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's afraid of that more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's from the West Blue.\NThere's no way of going back there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why those pirates he came here\Nwith are his only buddies and hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the scars on his forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he continues to hit his head hard\Nlike that, he'll die without doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange relationship, but\NI've been with him for 50 long years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stand by and watch him die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--What's that idiot doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we looked away for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he pretending he's mountain\Nclimbing or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Flower Arrangement!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a mast?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. It's from our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the main mast... Hey! Don't break the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He doesn't die\Neven when he's crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he think he's doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! What the hell are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm strong, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna defeat me, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fight isn't over yet!\NSo we have to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your buddies're dead,\Nbut I'm your rival forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely have to fight again\Nin order to decide who is stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After going around the Grand Line,\Nwe'll come back to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I come back, let's fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm. This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the symbol of our\Npromise to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we come back, don't remove that\Nmark by hitting your head. Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, flower pops! Thanks for the log pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, whale! I'm leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Whisky Peak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...full speed ahead!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy got him to stop killing himself\Nby hitting his head on the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, he's waiting for his\Ncrewmates back at those capes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unbelievable story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides have been keeping\Ntheir promise for fifty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea one of the people\NLaboon has been waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was that skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, have grown stronger\Nduring these past five years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We share the same thought patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you still hold your afro dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot possibly hope to\Ndefend such a large weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, do you still remember us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart grows tight\Nwhenever I think about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't have a heart anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were not strong enough to face\Nthe harsh cruelty of the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our friends have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, I lost everything along with\Nmy crewmates, including my face and body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we were to meet again,\Nyou probably wouldn't recognize me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:20:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now that I've been reduced to a skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt my afro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing left...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to protect this hair,\Nwhich everyone said resembled you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing them like this, they look just alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook's hair really resembles Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect the last remnant of who I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I will go see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like you to keep waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the capes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where we made our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love that bag of bones\Nand that whale, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a musician, a talking skeleton,\Nhas an afro, goes "Yo-ho ho!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was Laboon's pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming aboard our ship,\Neven if I have to drag him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's joining our crew! Any objections, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were, would you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna help him see Laboon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got my vote, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.98,0:22:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here, dummy!\NI'm not afraid of that skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a given. I'm more concerned\Nabout stopping Nami-san's marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to raid the place. Don't we\Nhave one more shadow to recover now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! Guys, get ready for our counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna knock\NThriller Bark outta the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go!\N--You're coming, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgiveable! Who's trying\Nto marry Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot to mention this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when Nami was in the bath,\Nthat invisible man--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?! Wh-Wh-What did\Nhe do when she was in the bath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked her up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Food, Nami, and Shadows!!\NLuffy's Enraged Counterattack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
